Title: Fires of Kiev: The Ukraine Revolution (Montage)
Description:
This isn't alternate history, but its still important. Ukraine is not just a lone event, Venezuela, and Thailand have all erupted into protests. This week is a break from Alternate History, but next week I will release the new Alternate country video.
